<main>
    <div class="section-one">
    <div class="container sct1">
<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="left-column">
        <div class="upper-wrapper">
            <h1>Conquer the Web with Short URLs.</h1>
            <p>Create short links, QR Codes, and Link-in-bio pages. Share them anywhere.</p>
        </div> 
        <div class="lower-wrapper">
            <a class="get-started" href="#">Get Started</a>
            
            <a href="#how-it-works" class="how-it-works">how it works ?</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right-column">
                <div class="decor-container">
                <div >
                <img  class="mac-menubar" src="images/mac-menubar.svg" alt="">
                </div>
                 <div class="s-bar">
                    <span class="sbar">https://www.shortify.com/<span>
                </div>
                </div>
                 

            <div class="fun-container">
                <div class="fun-buttons">
                    <button class="funl btn1 active">
                        <img class="link__icon link1" src="/images/link1.svg" alt="Link Icon">
                        <img class="link__icon link2" src="/images/link2.svg" alt="Link Icon">
                        Short Link
                    </button>
                    <button class="funl btn2">
                        <img class="qr__link qr1" src="images/qr.svg" alt="qr icon">
                        <img class="qr__link qr2" src="images/qr1.svg" alt="qr icon">
                        QR Code
                    </button>
                </div>

                <h2 class="f-header">Shorten a long link </h2>

                <div class="url-shortner">
                    <img class="link-icon" src="images/link.svg" alt="link icon">
            <div class="entry-side">
                <form action="" method="post"></form>
                <label for="fullUrl "></label>
                <input type="url" name="fullUrl" id="fullUrl" placeholder="Enter your link here!">
            </div>

                <button class="shorten-btn" type="submit">Shorten Now!</button>
                <p id="shortenedLink" class="hidden"></p>
                 </div>

            </div>

    
    </div>
</div>
        </div>
          
</div>

 <div class="section-two">
    <div class="container sct2">
        <div class="wrapper2">
            <div class="wleft-column">
               <div class="w-upper">
                <h1>Elevate Your Link Experience.
                </h1>
                <p>Our platform was built to help you make every point of connection between your content and audience ignite action.</p>
               </div>
               <div class="w-lower">
                <a href="#">Try Now!</a>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="wright-column">
                <div class="rec r1">
                    <h2>Simplified</h2>
                    <p>Easy and intuitive link shortening process, no technical skills required</p>
                    <div class="icon c1"><img class="rc1" src="images/tap.svg" alt=""></div>
                
                </div>
                <div class="rec r2">
                    <h2>Shareable</h2>
                    <p>Shortened links are easily shareable on various platforms.</p>
                    <div class="icon c2"><img class="rc2" src="images/share1.svg" alt="share icon"></div>

                </div>
                <div class="rec r3">
                    <h2>QR Codes</h2>
                    <p>Generate dynamic QR codes to reach offline audiences</p>
                    <div class="icon c3"><img class="rc3" src="images/qr1.svg" alt="qr code icon"></div>

                </div>
                <div class="rec r4">
                    <h2>Optimized</h2>
                    <p>Boost engagement with powerful short links</p>
                    <div class="icon c4"><img class="rc4" src="images/opt.svg" alt="optimization icon"></div>

                </div>
                
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <div class="trusted-by">
            <h2 class="t-by">Trusted by</h2>
            <div class="brand-icons">
                <div class="trb brand1"> <img class="bigfish" src="images/bigfish.svg" alt="bigfish logo"></div>
                <div class="trb brand2"><img class="novasol" src="images/nova.svg" alt="novasol logo"></div>
                <div class="trb brand3"><img class="marriott" src="images/mar.svg" alt="marriott"></div>
                <div class="trb brand4"><img class="monday" src="images/mon.svg" alt="monday.com logo"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

 </div>

<div class="section-three">
    <div class="container sct3">
        <div class="wrapper3">
            <div class="wr-upper">
                <div class="s3-left">
                    <h1>shorten and share your link now</h1>
                    <p>Start now, Shorten URLs. Generate QR Code
                        And Share it Now!</p>

                        <a class="last-btn" href="#">Get Started</a>
                </div>
                <div class="s3-right"><img src="images/component.svg" alt=""></div>
            </div>
            <div class="wr-lower" id="how-it-works">
              <div class="rect rt1">
                <div class="circl cir1">
                    <h2>1</h2>
                </div>
                <h1>enter your link</h1>
                <p>Paste your long link into the our platform, and watch it transform like a digital makeover.</p>
              </div>  
              <div class="rect rt2">
                <div class="circl cir2">
                    <h2>2</h2>
                </div>
            <h1>click shortener</h1>
            <p>With a click, your link gets shorter and snappier – ready to share with style!</p>
              </div>  
              <div class="rect rt3">
                <div class="circl cir3">
                    <h2>3</h2>
                </div>
              <h1> custom qr code</h1>
              <p>Want an extra touch of cool? Craft a custom QR code that's uniquely yours, like a secret symbol for your link.</p>
              </div>  
              <div class="rect rt4">
                <div class="circl cir4">
                    <h2>4</h2>
                </div>
               <h1>share it!</h1>
               <p>Now comes the fun part – share your fresh link or your special QR code. It's like passing a little piece of digital joy to others!</p>
              </div>  
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
